snippet.title: Ace: Hero How-To
snippet.description:
Strife's first Hero How-To will help you hop into the Arena and break the ice, with Ace!

Strife is the premier second generation Multiplayer Online Battle Arena (MOBA) by S2 Games and is currently in Closed Beta. Visit www.strife.com today to sign up for a Closed Beta key.
